channel.title: RsGod - 718/724, Looking For Developers&Testers
channel.description:
[center]Welcome To.....
[img]http://i884.photobucket.com/albums/ac47/king_todd/RsGodLogo.png[/img]
[size=18pt]We Will Be Online By: Unknown[/size]
-------------------------------------------- [b]Introduction[/b]
Welcome to our RsGod Development Team. We strive to succeed in all possibilitys in a Economized server, along with PvP. It will be worth applying with what we are going to create.
-------------------------------------------- [b]About Us[/b]
I was inspired by Runescape Private Server developing since I first discovered them, which was merely 4 years ago. I started with the revision 317, and worked my way up. I will be supplying a domain and the VPS when we are finally online, but I plan on releasing a Beta first.
-------------------------------------------- [b]Goals[/b]
;Our Goals are to supply;
[ul][li]A Fully Economized Server[/li] [li]Fully Working Combat system and PvP[/li] [li]Grand Exchange[/li] [li]All 24 Skills Working[/li] [li]Squeal Of Fortune[/li] [li]Players vs. Monsters[/li][/ul]
and much More.
------------------------------------ [b]What will the donations be towards?[/b]
Our donations we receive will be put towards a stable Virtual Private Server, Forums, Website, etc. to keep us up and running.
--------------------------------------------------- [b]Would you like to apply?[/b]
[code] In-Game Username/Forums Username you will be using: Skype: Age: Gender: Email Address: Position you are looking for: Coding Languages/Knowledge(If Applying for Rank): Your Current Time Zone you are living in: Why would you want to become active and part of our server: Suggestions: ------------Other Info Stated Below Here----------- [/code]
